78
00:04:51,174 --> 00:04:52,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu dia.</font>

79
00:04:52,809 --> 00:04:55,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo. Sudah waktunya bekerja.</font>

80
00:04:55,278 --> 00:04:56,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu aku.</font>

81
00:04:57,781 --> 00:05:01,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, uangku!</font>

82
00:05:01,084 --> 00:05:03,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu untuk membayar tagihan
