89
00:05:19,536 --> 00:05:20,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitu?</font>

90
00:05:21,738 --> 00:05:23,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu, kita juga sudah berakhir.</font>

91
00:05:23,506 --> 00:05:25,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu yang aku inginkan.</font>

92
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:32,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kita berakhir seperti ini?</font>

93
00:05:32,849 --> 00:05:34,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Salah satu dari kita...</font>

94
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:37,420
