105
00:06:25,368 --> 00:06:27,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati-hati.</font>

106
00:06:35,178 --> 00:06:36,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak...</font>

107
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:03,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, tidak. Tidak.</font>

108
00:07:03,339 --> 00:07:06,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya, iya. Iya.</font>

109
00:07:14,784 --> 00:07:16,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir.</font>

110
00:07:22,992 --> 00:07:25,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memasukinya sekali lagi.</font>

111
00:07:27,664 --> 00:07:29,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu...</font>

112
00:07:29,566 --> 00:07:31,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melakukannya dengan caraku.</font>

113
00:07:34,504 --> 00:07:37,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Udaranya sangat menyegarkan. Udara di sini...</font>

