115
00:07:45,615 --> 00:07:47,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kabarmu, bodoh?</font>

116
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:54,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya kau tidak makan dengan baik.</font>

117
00:07:56,793 --> 00:07:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Detektif Cha.</font>

118
00:07:58,695 --> 00:08:00,160
<font color=#FFFF00>4885.</font>

119
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Biarkan aku sendiri.</font>

120
00:08:03,066 --> 00:08:05,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bodoh./ Apa?</font>

121
00:08:07,103 --> 00:08:09,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa berakhir di sini?</font>

122
00:08:09,472 --> 00:08:11,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang ingin kau ubah?</font>

123
00:08:11,407 --> 00:08:14,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kita bisa sangat berbeda?/
Apa yang kau bicarakan?</font>

124
00:08:14,711 --> 00:08:16,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memperingatkanmu lagi.</font>

125
00:08:16,379 --> 00:08:18,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Urus dirimu sendiri.</font>

126
00:08:18,448 --> 00:08:20,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau aku akan menyingkirkanmu juga.</font>

127
00:08:27,524 --> 00:08:29,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak akan mudah.</font>

128
00:08:29,626 --> 00:08:32,720
