<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mirip saudara yang kukenal.</font>

135
00:08:50,613 --> 00:08:53,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa namanya? Doppelclanger.</font>

136
00:08:53,449 --> 00:08:55,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dia  bicarakan?/ Doppelclanger.</font>

137
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:57,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka benar ada.</font>

138
00:08:57,954 --> 00:09:00,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini luar biasa tapi masih terlalu sentimentil.</font>

139
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:02,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudku...</font>

140
00:09:02,892 --> 00:09:05,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk berbicara dengan wanita
