166
00:10:25,008 --> 00:10:27,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Ponselmu. Ponselmu, semuanya, ponselmu.</font>

167
00:10:27,644 --> 00:10:29,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Ponselku?/ Ponselku.</font>

168
00:10:29,612 --> 00:10:31,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus mendapatkan nomor ponselnya.</font>

169
